name: REVOLUTIONS ARE LED BY WHORES (not celebrities)
description: For centuries, sex workers have been at the forefront of social movements. We are the original feminists — and yet we are talked over, criminalized and stigmatized in the name of “feminism.” We fight because we have to, for things that make everyone more free. What do you really know about freedom? Are celebrity worship and influencer idolization going to get you there? // The guillotine, as a classic symbol of revolution, was drawn with Sharpies to allude to the celebrities who minted Sharpie drawings. Model is me, Cryptonatrix.
